# CyberSecurity

===================================================================================
Welcome to the CTOC Challenges:
===================================================================================
"You have been hacked" - does that line make your adrenaline pump? Does preventing 
breaches and malware thrill you? Do you want to win a ticket to a unique day of 
Cyber Security with IBM's experts, including a visit to the C-TOC simulation center on 
wheels? Then take these challenges and catch the flags! Best of luck. 

%---- Watch the C-TOC here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_4fZ6wYQFw ----%

- Your task is to find the flags in the attached files. 
- Flags are in the format Flag(Flag_Text) to be found within the files.
- There are three challenges plus a bonus one, the flags combined will form a
sentence. This is your final answer. 
	
%---- Submit your final answer here: https://forms.gle/pf3UsH22aAGrc1To7 ----%
(Note that also half a sentence can take you all the way to the truck if too few have 
managed to solve the challenges, always make a try!)

Hints and Spoilers are provided below ... if you're not really up to the challenge.

===================================================================================

